<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE section PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DocBook XML V4.5//EN" "../../../docbook-xml-4.5/docbookx.dtd">
<section id="menus.help">
  <title id="menus.help.title"><guimenu>Даведка</guimenu></title>

  <para>This menu gives you access to information that will help you make the
  best of OmegaT.</para>

  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry id="menus.help.user.manual">
      <term id="menus.help.user.manual.title"><guimenuitem>User
      Manual...</guimenuitem> <keycombo><keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Адчыняецца гэты дапаможнік у браўзэры па змаўчаньні.</para>
    </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.help.about">
      <term id="menus.help.about.title"><guimenuitem>Пра праграму…</guimenuitem></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Паказ зьвестак пра аўтарскае права, падзякі і ліцэнзію.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.help.last.changes">
      <term id="menus.help.last.changes.title"><guimenuitem>Апошнія зьмены…</guimenuitem></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Displays the list of new functionality, enhancements and bug fixes
        for each new release.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.help.log">
      <term id="menus.help.log.title"><guimenuitem>Часопіс…</guimenuitem></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Паказваецца бягучы файл часопіса. The title of the dialog reflects the file currently in use (which depends on the number of concurrently running OmegaT instances).</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.help.check.for.updates">
      <term id="menus.help.check.for.updates.title"><guimenuitem>Праверка абнаўленьняў…</guimenuitem></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Checks to see if a newer version of OmegaT is available.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>